    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 1st level, your unique DNA allows you to transform with much more ease than the average shinobi, reducing the strain it puts upon your chakra network. When casting a jutsu that alters your body (such as Transform or Advanced Transformation) or alters your Physical stats (Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution), it has its cost reduced by 1 to a minimum of 1. This reduction increases by 1 at 7th and 13th level, to a maximum of 3.</p>",
